carousel-caption new"> <h2>Family gets more</h2> <h3>Home furnishing tips and ideas <span>|</span> Events and workshops</h3> <a href="https://m2.ikea.com/in/en/ikea-family/membership/#membership-signup" class="btn btn-join">Join Now (It’s free)</a> </div> </div> --> </div> </div> </div> <div class="container"> <div class="row flex center mt60 mlr40" rel="comin_from: "> <div class="col-sm-6 plr40"> <div class="catalog"><img src="http://ikea.in/themes/ikea/images/day-care-at-work.jpg" alt="" class="w100"></div> </div> <div class="col-sm-6 plr40"> <div class="home-content"> <h3>An initiative that cares</h3> <p>Introducing children's day-care benefit for all IKEA co-workers. Yes, for moms and dads alike! Now, parents can work peacefully knowing that their little ones are always safe and having fun, close by.</p> <p>Coming back to work just became a whole lot easier!</p> <a href="http://ikea.in/news">Know More</a> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row flex center mt60 mlr40 xs-flex" rel="comin_from: creating_life_better"> <div class="col-sm-6 plr40"> <div class="home-content"> <h3>Home Furnishings by IKEA</h3> <p>At IKEA, we know your home is more than just furniture. It is where your day begins and ends. It is a place where everyday moments become special - where dreams become a reality.</p> <p>IKEA home furnishing is beautiful, functional and affordable. Every product we create is our way of making your home a better, more comforatble place. We offer solutions for everyday life from furniture to furnishings, all under one roof.</p> <a href="http://ikea.in/about">More about IKEA</a> </div> </div> <div class="col-sm-6 plr40"> <div class="catalog"><img src="http://ikea.in/themes/ikea/hej/images/ikea-perspective.jpg" alt="" class="w100"></div> </div> </div> <div class="row flex center mt60 mlr40" rel="comin_from: a_culture_of_hearts"> <div class="col-sm-6 plr40"> <div class="catalog"><img src="http://ikea.in/themes/ikea/images/section41.png" alt="" class="w100"></div> </div> <div class="col-sm-6 plr40"> <div class="home-content"> <h3>A culture of hearts</h3> <p>The culture at IKEA is hard to describe but easy to embrace. It’s enthusiasm, togetherness and willpower, is born from our roots in southern Sweden and inspired by the IKEA founder, Ingvar Kamprad.</p> <p>The IKEA way of doing things unites us in our work to make everyday better and more beautiful. We extend this dedication and warmth to each of our customers and teammates. </p> <a href="http://ikea.in/jobs">More about Jobs</a> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="container"> <div class="row flex center mlr40 mb60 mt60 xs-flex"> <div class="col-sm-6 plr40"> <div class="home-content"> <h3>IKEA Hej HOME<br>An Interactive Experience Zone</h3> <p>Say hello to IKEA and experience beautiful home furnishing solutions at #IKEAHejHome, Forum Mall, Hyderabad from 22nd November onwards.</p> <p>Get a sneak peek into the world of IKEA months before the store opening in Hyderabad where you can finally buy these products.</p> <a href="http://ikea.in/HejHome">Know More</a> </div> </div> <div class="col-sm-6 plr40"> <div class="catalog"><img src="http://ikea.in/themes/ikea/images/experience-zone.jpg" alt="" class="w100"></div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="container"> <div class="ikea-jobs"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-sm-7"> <h3>Join us in creating a brighter everyday life for India!</h3> </div> <div class="col-sm-5 text-right"> <a href="http://ikea.in/jobs">See Available Jobs</a> </div> </div> </div> </div> <!-- <div class="modal fade video_popup" id="video_popup" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel"> <div class="modal-dialog" role="document"> <div class="modal-content"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button> <div class="modal-body"> <iframe src="https://iframe.dacast.com/b/101713/c/455811" width="100%" height="426" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen webkitallowf